~ scene_2_high
Marcos: I understand this may be worrying for you. For your peace of mind, your customer number ends in 4582, right? 
Marcos: Don’t worry, I’m not going to ask for any personal information. We just want to help you protect your computer. These issues are quite common.
do update_trust(20)
Personaje: Oh, yes, yes… that’s right, it ends with those numbers. Thank you very much for knowing it! 
Personaje: Sorry for being distrustful, but I’m not used to these scares anymore… Tell me, what should I do?
=> scene_3

~ scene_2_neutral
